                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18090412-8-defend84 t18090412-8-punish40"></join>
               fined One Shilling
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>First Middlesex jury, before Mr. justice Le Blanc.</p>


